  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said on certain Saturday to come at such, such hour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't-- because I couldn't tell the farmers that I need-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after I was inducted, also he told me that I cannot work in the-- on a farm--",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Because the Germans, or many people capable to work, naturally physically, building roads and they inducted in the, their engineering units which were called TODD, T-O-D-D.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It doesn't mean death, but then this is after the name of the general who was in charge of those units like SS units or as other troop [? not-- ?] this was called Todd [?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Troopen. ?] And they inducted civilian to those units.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because I was in these territories--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would have to be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So to be protected, they gave me-- was also in the same village, way on the hill, was a big [INAUDIBLE], big farm, and this belonged before the war to a Polish general.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after, when the Communists came, they nationalized naturally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the Germans came, they put a administrator, administrator on that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I get that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had the job over that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was put in charge of fish hatcheries because they had ponds, man-made ponds, square ponds where they raised fish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the fish were supposed to go to German army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't-- not-- we-- they couldn't sell to any civilian store or to any civilian people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All they-- because this was a national property, this is a German property.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All the fish had to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We could have for our own use, but all of the other would be delivered to a depot to a General.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But unfortunate, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we never delivered any fish.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
